{
  "message": "Add v2, v3, and near-miss parser corpus test fixtures\n\nExpand the Claude Code parser test corpus with 32 new fixture files\n(16 input .txt + 16 expected .expect.json pairs) covering:\n\nv2 variants:\n- api_key_error_v2, approval_needed_v2, context_warning_v2,\n  cost_summary_v2, network_error_v2, session_end_v2, thinking_v2,\n  timeout_error_v2, tool_use_v2\n\nv3 variants:\n- tool_use_v3 (multi-tool invocation format)\n\nNear-miss variants:\n- api_key_error_near_miss, approval_needed_near_miss,\n  context_warning_near_miss, cost_summary_near_miss,\n  network_error_near_miss, session_end_near_miss\n\nNear-miss fixtures test that the parser correctly rejects inputs that\nlook superficially similar to a pattern but differ in key structural\ndetails, preventing false-positive detections.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
